ss=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c45c382976afb8e25a6b8ed711ae1e40911a7933","tid":2328803,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"60fc72e9f6fb4da546af67f9a2e6b24299d3d4b4","tid":2328803,"uid":894,"like":9,"dislike":5,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T19:40:39.000Z","msg":"其實唔明三色豆有咩難食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n芫荽都話有陣臭味唔係個個鍾意"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T20:35:53.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">三色蔬菜裏頭都是澱粉，那麼「抗性澱粉」是怎麼來的呢？原來經煮熟流程後，急速在負30-45度間的低溫冷凍中，三色蔬菜中大部分的「直鏈澱粉」分子結構被改變，變成不易被吸收消化的「抗性澱粉」！</code></pre><br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">咬破三色蔬菜裏頭粉粉的口感，主因就是這些「抗性澱粉」加上冷凍失水後的纖維組織！更別說青豆和玉米嚼不爛的外皮了～噁。</code></pre><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2743/2743657.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2743%2F2743657.jpg&h=eac484b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/amp/lemon_amp_news.php?lemon_news_id=29232&amp;from=google.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Famp%2Flemon_amp_news.php%3Flemon_news_id%3D29232%26from%3Dgoogle.com&d=c%2B6PkbrQ5MzYtHY5m9tE13fp3ZHOIdf2SFoQnphXrww%3D&h=fad690d2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/amp/lemon_amp_news.php?lemon_news_id=29232&amp;from=google.com</a>"},{"pid":"7df2230de77b30e32401280ecfee7a43668d19ba","tid":2328803,"uid":129013,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T20:38:03.000Z","msg":"三色豆入面嘅青豆先係大魔王"},{"pid":"a2d3962c8bce528b6f068a6ed0dfbc463966772d","tid":2328803,"uid":286131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7df2230de77b30e32401280ecfee7a43668d19ba","tid":2328803,"uid":129013,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T20:38:03.000Z","msg":"三